00:17:06.160 --> 00:17:07.960
Preesha..

00:17:14.080 --> 00:17:16.800
Alhamdulillah.. Preesha..

00:17:19.080 --> 00:17:22.080
Apakah kamu baik-baik saja?  Apakah kamu terluka?

00:17:23.720 --> 00:17:24.720
Apakah kamu baik-baik saja?

00:17:27.320 --> 00:17:28.320
Rudra..

